<D>__{the priest. did they release his name?}
<C>__{sibeal}
<D>__{no. but i made a few calls, still got some friends in the diocese there. mckinney. father douglas mckinney.}
<A>__{the boys flash with recognition.}
<C>__{sibeal }
<D>__{you knew him?}
<C>__{connor}
<D>__{knew of him. everybody did. a regular mother theresa. youth hostels, soup kitchens. even made it into the newspapers sometimes.}
<A>__{sibeal considers this. he genuflects and turns.}
